    "description": "The Battlefield DLC contains a new environment for the Bulanci game with several game maps for various game modes and number of players. The Battlefield environment includes a slew of new game mechanisms, which brings the game tactics to yet another level.<br>If you purchase the Battlefield DLC on Steam, you will be entitled to receive free updates.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >New mechanisms</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>1. Heavy rotary minigun with unlimited ammo.<br></li><li>2. Air bombs which randomly fall on the battlefield and force players to change vantage points.<br></li><li>3. The effect of strong wind which influences players’ walking speed, unless they hide in trenches.<br></li><li>4. Narrow trenches which protect from both strong wind and the heavy minigun fire, but prevent evade maneuvers.</li></ul>",
